      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single ASTM F1717 standard condition (70 mm interbody distance, room temperature, quasi-static 1 mm/min). Only one load condition evaluated; no variation in fixture offset or temperature. This limits generalizability but is consistent with the COU scope (single-condition regulatory submission). Achieved Gradation 2 is below required Gradation 3 — identified as a known gap; mitigated by tight acceptance bounds and conservative material properties.",
